text: John Seymour (1474 - 1536) was the father of Henry VIII's third wife Jane Seymour. He married a young English woman named Margery Wentworth. He was born on the year 1476 (exact date is unknown) and died the year Jane Seymour wed Henry VIII in 1536 at the age 62. Category:English knights Category:1474 births Category:1536 deaths
